Note on third-party material bundled with this repository:

- `EU_AI_Act_guides/OJ_L_202401689_EN_TXT.pdf` and other regulatory PDFs are
  reproductions of EU official publications (Regulation 2024/1689). EU
  legislative texts are publicly available; the PDFs retain their original
  distribution terms (see https://eur-lex.europa.eu/).
- `Checklists y ejemplos/*.xlsx` and `Ejemplo de hoja de AUDITORIA_HUMANA.xlsx`
  are derived from AESIA implementation guidance and are included as reference
  material; consult the original sources for authoritative content.
- `Informes_Cursos_Anthropic/` material derives from publicly distributed
  Anthropic course material; refer to Anthropic's documentation for the
  authoritative source.
- `prompt_architect/` is a co-located dependency skill; treat it as read-only
  inside this repository. Upstream lives under its own version line.

This MIT license applies to the original generator code, prompts, references,
templates, wizard, dashboard, tests, and documentation authored within this
repository.
